General Information

Contains vitamins that assist in maintaining energy levels. Contains nutrients that supports healthy nervous system. Supports healthy muscles and bones. Contains Vitamin A that supports eye health.

Warnings

Always read the label; take only as directed. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Not to be used in children under two years of age without medical advice.

Common Uses

General wellbeing

Ingredients

Each Gummy contains: Vitamin A 200 micrograms Vitamin E 6 mg Vitamin D 2.5 microgram Niacinamide 8 mg Pyridoxine Hydrochloride 700 microgram Biotin 25 microgram Folic Acid 100 microgram Vitamin B12 1.25 microgram Ascorbic Acid 40 mg Iodine 22.5 microgram Zinc 1.5mg

Directions

Children 2-8 years: 2 gummies per day. Children 8+ years: 3 gummies per day. Or as directed by your healthcare professional.
